{"tid":1540932,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"重要時刻!!向美國表達香港極需要有監查、有懲罰機制的民主法案","createTime":"2019-09-04T12:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:13:11.000Z","uid":267959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6192e9a9596d25054fac852924f27830aadd5c67","tid":1540932,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:57:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>重要時刻!!</strong></span>時間不太夠  9月9日美國復會<br />\n香港人必須向美國國會表達我們極度需要一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有監查、有懲罰機制</span></span>的民主法案<br />\n雖然現在有1.3個訴求好像答應了，外國可能以為問題已經解決，香港人的民怨退潮，但<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警濫權</span></span></strong>跟之後來的<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">信用系統</span></span></strong>仍係香港人頭上一把刀<br />\n轉戰文書確是現在首要工作﹕<br />\n1. G20文宣可以在9月9日重點在美國報紙登廣告提出香港人需要民主法案<br />\n2. 可以幫忙開個白宮連署 (我英文不太好，怕發了會詞不達意)<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，香港急需有監查、有懲罰機制的民主法案<br />\n3. 其他人可以透過Twitter, FB 跟美國人表達香港仍在泥沼中<br />\n兄弟爬山，遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1317604afdd67c63b9f35a3417dff08a7f8fd7","tid":1540932,"uid":148775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"改左新版 希望可以幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打左篇文講少少關於 五大訴求 缺一不可，希望大家可以幫推同share比外國人睇 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[國際線][English][4-9-2019] Five Demands, Not One Less!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540646\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540646</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c0093dc5b1306ec93c14cb3d424452291e32cf12","tid":1540932,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T12:58:46.000Z","msg":"20"},{"pid":"6f178489f988087c3e1daaafe432cd